âœ… Delete all â€” Double-click the DELETE ALL button to clear all saved links.

âœ… Persistent storage â€” Uses localStorage to keep your links safe.

âš™ï¸ How to Use
Clone or download this repository.

Add a manifest.json file if not present (with proper permissions).

